by javiereguiluz at 2015-12-07T08:15:57Z

@aimeos thanks for adding this project to the list. Before merging the changes, I'd like to ask you to make two changes:

1) The icon must be in a square format, because otherwise it will look ugly when resizing it (this is an example of the page where it will be displayed: http://symfony.com/components/HttpFoundation)
2) The description must be just one paragraph(you currently propose three paragraphs).

If you need more help, you can check out how does a project called Elcodi do it, because it's similar to your project: logo (https://github.com/symfony/symfony-marketing/blob/master/projects/elcodi.png), description (https://github.com/symfony/symfony-marketing/blob/master/projects/en/elcodi.html.twig). Thanks.

