by aimeos at 2015-12-07T11:43:10Z

@javiereguiluz We've changed the paragraphs and use a square image now. The long text is hard to read if it's not split in paragraphs, so maybe it would be a good idea to allow more than one in the future.

BTW: Aimeos is very similar to Sylius too but not only available for Symfony :-)

