@aimeos thanks for making the changes. I'm afraid I have to make another request: the *"one paragraph-only rule"* is precisely set to prevent long descriptions. It's not a matter of putting the three paragraphs of text in a single `<p>` but a matter of writing only one paragraph. So, could you please remove some text to make the description shorter (similar to the rest of the projects). Thanks!
